name: Lens studio
description:
AR-First Developer Platform

With a robust set of features to empower creativity, if you can dream it, you can build it. Create viral selfie Lenses and shoppable try-on experiences, or develop never-before-seen ways of connecting with the world around you for an audience of millions. With zero setup time and seamless integration with Snapchat, Spectacles, and your mobile and web applications, you can build AR for anywhere.
